# mbuf_free

**Function**

## Declaration

```swift
mbuf_t mbuf_free(mbuf_t mbuf);
```

## Parameters

- **mbuf**: The mbuf to free.

## Return Value

The next mbuf in the chain.

## Discussion

Frees a single mbuf. Not commonly used because it doesn't touch the rest of the mbufs on the chain.
